 "remarks": "Rare. Exceptional. Timeless. Hidden away on a private two-acre cul-de-sac where Westover meets Greenwich, this Mid-Century Modern estate is a masterclass in light, height, and form. Designed for an inspired lifestyle, the main residence boasts five spacious bedrooms and four-and-a-half baths, defined by sweeping architectural lines and massive expanses of glass that look out over the Mianus River. A true compound for creatives and entertainers alike, the property features a spectacular detached pool house complete with a kitchen, lofted bedroom, and full bath-perfect for multigenerational living or an ultra-private guest suite. A vintage greenhouse, detached two-car garage, and a storied history of artistic residents complete this unparalleled sanctuary. Live where nature and iconic design completely converge.",
